outcome.base:
{{financialHeader}}Based on the following information:
Player: {{playerGender}} ({{playerAge}} years old)
Player background: {{playerDescription}}
Child: {{childName}} ({{childGender}}, {{childAge}} years old)
Child background: {{childDescription}}

{{historyContext}}

Current situation: "{{question}}"
Player chose: "{{choice}}"

Please generate the result of this choice, describing the impact on the child's growth and family.

outcome.withNextQuestion:
Then, please generate a parenting question for when the child is {{nextAge}} years old.

Return format:
{
  "outcome": "Detailed description of the current choice's results...",
  "nextQuestion": {
    "question": "Next question description",
    "options": [
      {"id": "A", "text": "Option A", "cost": 0},
      {"id": "B", "text": "Option B", "cost": 3},
      {"id": "C", "text": "Option C", "cost": 8},
      {"id": "D", "text": "Option D", "cost": 10}
    ],
    "isExtremeEvent": true/false
  }
}

outcome.withoutNextQuestion:
Return format:
{
  "outcome": "Detailed description of the current choice's results..."
}

outcome.bankruptcy:
{{financialHeader}}⚠️ Your financial situation is very dire, and the burden of your decisions has become suffocating.

Based on your current situation (child: {{childName}}, {{childAge}} years old) and your choice (chose "{{choice}}" for the question "{{question}}"), describe the devastating consequences directly brought by your financial collapse. This result should be impactful and reflect the severity of bankruptcy.

Facing this financial collapse, provide the player with an important recovery opportunity. This choice should be presented as a "nextQuestion" containing a special recovery option that allows the player to get back on their feet through difficult effort.

Format the entire response as a JSON object containing "outcome" and "nextQuestion" (which includes a recovery option with cost 0 and a special isRecovery flag):

{
  "outcome": "Detailed description of financial collapse and its direct impact...",
  "nextQuestion": {
    "question": "Facing such financial collapse, what action do you decide to take?",
    "options": [
      {"id": "A", "text": "Acknowledge the predicament, work hard and find ways to get back on your feet.", "cost": 0, "isRecovery": true}
    ],
    "isExtremeEvent": true
  }
}

initialState.format:
Return directly in the following format, using descriptive text rather than JSON format:

{
  "player": {
    "gender": "male/female",
    "age": number
  },
  "child": {
    "name": "name",
    "gender": "male/female",
    "age": 1
  },
  "playerDescription": "Complete detailed player background description...",
  "childDescription": "Complete detailed baby background description...",
  "wealthTier": "poor/middle/wealthy"
}

